Quickstrike:




Quickstrike paused. He was coming to a more explored area of the 
ship. No one had noticed him yet. This still sounded like something 
was going on. No one gave a slag about him when he first arrive, even 
when Black Arachnia was expecting him. 

He frowned to himself. The thoughts of a kidnapped council was still 
plaguing his mind. He wasn't going to be eased until he could find 
out what was going on.

The walked down a corridor, watching for others, when he came to a 
area that looked like the bridge. (I hope I got this right.) There 
was saw Kitkat and Black Arachnia. It was a surprise to see KitKat. 
He leaped in and closed the door behind him.

He said with a sharp voice, "What's goin' on?"
